    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>摊开手牌，手指扣扳机</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将<strong>战术卡组构筑</strong>与<strong>第一人称精确射击</strong>锐利融合。选择你的卡牌、打造协同，用一发子弹完成合同——<strong>每一发都至关重要</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332120/extras/e1de229d67e99c104010e0f357689bd3.poster.avif?t=1770062654\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332120/extras/e1de229d67e99c104010e0f357689bd3.webm?t=1770062654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332120/extras/e1de229d67e99c104010e0f357689bd3.mp4?t=1770062654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>你会爱上的理由！</strong></u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“决定并开枪”的战术动作</strong>——出牌、读懂战场态势，在恰当时机切入 FPS 完成击杀。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>机制间的动态切换</strong>——从俯视角射击切换到 FPS，或反之亦然。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每个任务都有惊喜</strong>——全新敌人、模式与机制让探索始终新鲜。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>强大的黑手党头目</strong>——各自地盘有独特规则、陷阱与强敌。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roguelite 地图与进程</strong>——在敌人、小头目、事件、支线与安全屋之间择路，步步逼近 Big Boss。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>弹药有限</strong>——管理子弹是策略（也是压力）的一部分。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>副武器</strong>——用不同方式解决目标并节省弹药。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>短局可反复游玩</strong>——“再来一把”的最佳长度（平均 8–15 分钟）。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332120/extras/e8961032f21e8200a19f4e511f3390eb.poster.avif?t=1770062654\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332120/extras/e8961032f21e8200a19f4e511f3390eb.webm?t=1770062654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332120/extras/e8961032f21e8200a19f4e511f3390eb.mp4?t=1770062654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>探索这款游戏</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是黑手党地下世界的赏金猎人。凭借致命卡组与可靠步枪，每一份合同都是一场神经对决：连锁效果、制造破绽，在一切有利时扣动扳机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每次任务前构筑你的狩猎卡组。卡牌在<strong>开局即生效</strong>并塑造战场：<strong>防弹衣、额外弹药、防护</strong>等加成为那一记完美射击铺路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332120/extras/a0af459a765cf021de124b559de347ad.poster.avif?t=1770062654\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332120/extras/a0af459a765cf021de124b559de347ad.webm?t=1770062654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332120/extras/a0af459a765cf021de124b559de347ad.mp4?t=1770062654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>黑手党头目</u></strong> 头目各自掌控领地。看穿其行动模式，打出最后一击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332120/extras/8547bd8a2f495aa53cfcf2b3cc70c03e.poster.avif?t=1770062654\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332120/extras/8547bd8a2f495aa53cfcf2b3cc70c03e.webm?t=1770062654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332120/extras/8547bd8a2f495aa53cfcf2b3cc70c03e.mp4?t=1770062654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>副武器</u></strong> 多变、迅速、节省（弹药）、决定性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332120/extras/7dcd15cd72c4f25203f3cf8df33b9a28.poster.avif?t=1770062654\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332120/extras/7dcd15cd72c4f25203f3cf8df33b9a28.webm?t=1770062654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332120/extras/7dcd15cd72c4f25203f3cf8df33b9a28.mp4?t=1770062654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>进程与地图</u></strong> 在敌人、小头目、事件、支线任务与安全屋之间规划路线；每片区域最终直面一位头目——掌控领地，直指 Big Boss。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332120/extras/1ee59d9929c6ff240d727a29d9699821.poster.avif?t=1770062654\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332120/extras/1ee59d9929c6ff240d727a29d9699821.webm?t=1770062654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332120/extras/1ee59d9929c6ff240d727a29d9699821.mp4?t=1770062654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>社区</strong></u> 想参与开发、加入试玩并获取活动福利？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎加入我们的 Discord <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332120/extras/d20a1a613c054d517370cc133d421395.avif?t=1770062654\" width=1200 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
